[
    {
        "text": "Hello, welcome to Michael's Better Business English.",
        "startTime": 743,
        "endTime": 3377,
        "slowStartTime": 1264,
        "slowEndTime": 5290
    },
    {
        "text": "This month, we're looking at how to persuade people.",
        "startTime": 3987,
        "endTime": 6687,
        "slowStartTime": 6130,
        "slowEndTime": 10256
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, I'm sure this is difficult in Japanese as well as in English.",
        "startTime": 7455,
        "endTime": 11106,
        "slowStartTime": 11333,
        "slowEndTime": 16884
    },
    {
        "text": "However, here are three techniques to help you persuade people effectively.",
        "startTime": 11685,
        "endTime": 15976,
        "slowStartTime": 17677,
        "slowEndTime": 24189
    },
    {
        "text": "First, logical technique.",
        "startTime": 17010,
        "endTime": 19193,
        "slowStartTime": 25665,
        "slowEndTime": 29015
    },
    {
        "text": "Now here, when we are trying to persuade somebody logically,...",
        "startTime": 19948,
        "endTime": 22773,
        "slowStartTime": 30072,
        "slowEndTime": 34384
    },
    {
        "text": "...we give very clear reasons why they should accept our argument.",
        "startTime": 23246,
        "endTime": 27168,
        "slowStartTime": 35019,
        "slowEndTime": 40977
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, we often use data, figures, statistics to support what we're saying.",
        "startTime": 27806,
        "endTime": 32286,
        "slowStartTime": 41859,
        "slowEndTime": 48654
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, \"Over 80% of our customers prefer this design.\"",
        "startTime": 33027,
        "endTime": 37419,
        "slowStartTime": 49691,
        "slowEndTime": 56354
    },
    {
        "text": "\"That's why I recommend it.\"",
        "startTime": 37983,
        "endTime": 39229,
        "slowStartTime": 57124,
        "slowEndTime": 59068
    },
    {
        "text": "Secondly, win-win approach.",
        "startTime": 40559,
        "endTime": 42629,
        "slowStartTime": 60988,
        "slowEndTime": 64169
    },
    {
        "text": "This one stresses the mutual benefits:...",
        "startTime": 43196,
        "endTime": 45832,
        "slowStartTime": 64944,
        "slowEndTime": 68973
    },
    {
        "text": "...the benefits to both parties.",
        "startTime": 46173,
        "endTime": 48165,
        "slowStartTime": 69410,
        "slowEndTime": 72473
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, \"Now this option is good for you and good for us.\"",
        "startTime": 48794,
        "endTime": 53253,
        "slowStartTime": 73341,
        "slowEndTime": 80104
    },
    {
        "text": "Third approach is the emotional approach.",
        "startTime": 54985,
        "endTime": 57703,
        "slowStartTime": 82627,
        "slowEndTime": 86779
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, you're trying to persuade by playing on the feelings of the listener.",
        "startTime": 58062,
        "endTime": 62623,
        "slowStartTime": 87243,
        "slowEndTime": 94160
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, this could be through sympathy.",
        "startTime": 63358,
        "endTime": 65596,
        "slowStartTime": 95187,
        "slowEndTime": 98619
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Oh, you know how hard I've been working recently.\"",
        "startTime": 66478,
        "endTime": 69683,
        "slowStartTime": 99867,
        "slowEndTime": 104750
    },
    {
        "text": "\"That's why I need a bigger bonus.\"",
        "startTime": 70085,
        "endTime": 71957,
        "slowStartTime": 105278,
        "slowEndTime": 108161
    },
    {
        "text": "Or through empathy, when they understand your situation.",
        "startTime": 72994,
        "endTime": 76639,
        "slowStartTime": 109641,
        "slowEndTime": 115183
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, \"I'm sure you had the same difficulty yourself when you joined the company.\"",
        "startTime": 77476,
        "endTime": 82746,
        "slowStartTime": 116364,
        "slowEndTime": 124344
    },
    {
        "text": "\"That's why you understand my situation.\"",
        "startTime": 83295,
        "endTime": 85359,
        "slowStartTime": 125092,
        "slowEndTime": 128263
    },
    {
        "text": "So, when you need to persuade someone, remember these approaches.",
        "startTime": 87087,
        "endTime": 91078,
        "slowStartTime": 130781,
        "slowEndTime": 136842
    },
    {
        "text": "Often combining two or even three approaches,...",
        "startTime": 91475,
        "endTime": 95195,
        "slowStartTime": 137363,
        "slowEndTime": 143018
    },
    {
        "text": "...that will really help you persuade people more effectively.",
        "startTime": 95518,
        "endTime": 98253,
        "slowStartTime": 143427,
        "slowEndTime": 147605
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you and good luck!",
        "startTime": 99398,
        "endTime": 100647,
        "slowStartTime": 149247,
        "slowEndTime": 151196
    }
]